{"type":"message","id":"0be53ef8","parentId":"988e8945","timestamp":"2026-04-12T07:45:23.612Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good. No subagents are active. The 5p Status Report subagent appears to have completed (its status isn't \"failed\"). Let me check the time:\n\n- Current time: 07:44 UTC = 14:44 UTC+7 (but wait, the HEARTBEAT says morning briefing at 07:20 AM UTC+7, which would be 00:20 UTC). Current time is 07:44 UTC = 14:44 UTC+7. So it's afternoon UTC+7.\n\nActually wait, the HEARTBEAT says \"Morning Briefing — 07:20 AM UTC+7\" and \"night silence is 23:00–07:00 UTC+7\". Current time is 07:44 UTC = 14:44 UTC+7. \n\nSo it's definitely daytime in UTC+7, meaning I'm outside the night silence window. Now looking at the session list: the main heartbeat session is running, there's a subagent running the 5p status report, and the cron session that spawned it is done. The HEARTBEAT's \"Every ~5 min — Presence Broadcast\" section says to send a presence table whenever there are active sessions, so I should format and send that now.\n\nBuilding the presence table... I'm seeing the rest of the Telegram status updates, and since I'm awake and it's morning, I should send out a briefing report along with the status updates to both the direct message and the group chat.","thinkingSignature":"2915c5cd961d884e59a2f93b945cd5e1c4a0f607aae2a9837f900b6950551745"},{"type":"text","text":"Active sessions detected. Building presence board + morning briefing.\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_fctjgdxofw6g_1","name":"sessions_send","arguments":{"sessionKey":"agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:direct:6053576134","message":"🌅 Morning Pipeline Report — 12/04\n\nActive sessions: 4/34\nPipeline: HEALTHY ✅\n\nSessions:\n• master-orchestrator  → running (heartbeat)\n• 5p Status Report     → running (subagent, spawned by cron)\n• cron: 5p Progress    → done (last run 07:35 UTC)\n• telegram:group       → done (last run 07:31 UTC)\n• telegram: