{"type":"message","id":"f680afc3","parentId":"21809f61","timestamp":"2026-04-12T07:46:20.148Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Lead is asking what's next. Let me check MEMORY.md for pending tasks and any open items.\n\nFrom MEMORY.md:\n- Pending: Stitch MCP async polling wrapper + stitch-connect skill update\n- Completed: students page filter bug, cron jobs, duplicate tokens, exposed tokens\n\nBut Lead is talking about Confluence MCP and GitLab MCP being added. This sounds like a new task or something that happened in a conversation I don't have full context for. Let me check memory for recent context about this.","thinkingSignature":"c1332e3ddc250326a34755bfac4b4a7f1ee8cbee0c4447fd0e5a255d3aa86e80"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_26kqs5n09x9i_1","name":"memory_search","arguments":{"query":"Confluence MCP GitLab MCP gateway restart"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":0,"output":135,"cacheRead":5202,"cacheWrite":10027,"totalTokens":15364,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775979974759,"responseId":"062a80c88cc011881d6ca0d7ec512570"}}
